About Java I/O package


The java.io package contains nearly every class
you might ever need to perform input and output (I/O) in Java.

All these streams represent an input source and an output destination.
The stream in the java.io package supports many data such as primitives, object, localized characters, etc.


Java.io package provides classes for system input and output
through data streams, serialization and the file system.
This reference will take you through simple and practical methods available in java.io package.